summary: Donald Trump's Secret Service code name - The “Mogul” code name, assigned to Donald Trump by the United States Secret Service, encapsulates the essence of his larger-than-life persona and business empire. As a prominent figure in real estate, television, and politics, Trump’s influence has been far-reaching and undeniable. The term “Mogul” not only reflects his business acumen but also his assertive and bold approach to leadership and decision-making. This code name became a symbol of his ambitious drive to reshape the American landscape, both economically and politically. Embracing the spirit of “Mogul,” we introduce a new meme coin on the Ethereum blockchain—MOGUL. Inspired by Trump’s iconic status and the ethos of making bold moves, MOGUL aims to bring a community-driven growth to the crypto space. If you’re a supporter of Trump’s legacy, this coin represents a unique opportunity to be part of a dynamic and influential movement in the crypto space.
